{
  "texts": [
    "Detecting hallucination on-the-fly remains a daunting task.",
    "Language models tend to over-commit to early mistakes, leading to more errors and contributing to hallucination snowballing (Zhang et al., 2023).",
    "Improving Reliability Techniques to improve LLMs' reliability and reduce uncertainty have been proposed in the literature (Zhou et al., 2023).",
    "Wang et al.",
    "(Wang et al., 2022) found that sampling and aggregating multiple chain-of-thought reasoning paths can enhance LLMs' performance and reliability."
  ]
}